STEP 17 — AUTOMATIC RISK GOVERNANCE ENGINE
========================================================

Automatically reduce deployment when:

• Account drawdown increases

• Portfolio concentration increases

• Portfolio heat exceeds limits

• Opportunity quality deteriorates

• Execution survivability deteriorates

• Event risk increases

• Volatility expands materially

Automatically reject deployment when:

• Opportunity rejected

• Execution unsafe

• Portfolio capacity exhausted

• Account in critical condition

• Maximum exposure limits exceeded

