UNIVERSAL PRINCIPLE
========================================================

A profitable trade does not justify excessive risk.

A losing trade does not mean deployment was incorrect.

Correct deployment is determined by process, not outcome.

Capital should never be deployed because it is available.

Capital should only be deployed because it is deserved.

